value.0: This appears to be the uniform of a Czerka Corporation employee.

Vek Sorn is a weathered Duros with cracked blue skin and deep-set, crimson eyes that have seen more than their share of trouble. She runs a decrepit apartment complex  in the Korriban Wastes. The building is barely standingrusted durasteel beams jut out like broken bones, flickering wall sconces cast eerie shadows, and the air always carries the scent of dust, ozone, and old death.
A good sauce pan is every cook's friend.  Both for boiling potatoes, and restoring order. Grab this pan, open one can of whoop-ass, and do lunch!
